folder: Cornell Avenue & Bolton Avenue, Bronx, NY
text:
Cornell Avenue, east of Bolton Avenue, showing the Monnot House. It stood in the middle of Cornell Avenue. It was torn down between 1923 and 1927.
Views 1, 2:  1914
View 3: June 17, 1923
